OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774795970
OL,3,CBody of a woman found in River Ouse
OL,5,FThe body of a woman has been found in
OL,6,Fthe River Ouse.
OL,8,FHer body was recovered from the water
OL,9,Fnear Cawood at around 12pm on Thursday
OL,10,Fby police working on an unconnected
OL,11,Finvestigation in the area.
OL,13,FOfficers said the death is being
OL,14,Ftreated as unexplained.
OL,16,FNorth Yorkshire Police are
OL,17,Finvestigating when and where she
OL,18,Fentered the river.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
