OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1774795970
OL,3,CBody of a woman found in River Ouse
OL,5,FIn a statement, the force said:
OL,6,F"Extensive enquiries are ongoing to
OL,7,Festablish her identity and the
OL,8,Fcircumstances that led to her being in
OL,9,Fthe water including where and when she
OL,10,Fentered the river.
OL,12,F"At this stage we are unable to
OL,13,Frelease any further information but
OL,14,Fwill keep you updated when we are in a
OL,15,Fposition to do so."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
